apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, two men are shown holding hands, one with a dark skin tone and the other with a medium-dark skin tone, their fingers intertwined with a natural, tactile quality. Apple’s signature smooth gradients and realistic lighting give the emoji a sense of warmth and genuine connection, celebrating diversity and partnership. This emoji is a powerful symbol of love, friendship, and solidarity between men, often used to express support or celebrate relationships.
